features: Women’s specific tapered rectangular shape for comfort and versatility
RDS 650+ Loft ULTRA-DRY Down™ offers excellent insulation and compressibility
Extra down fill and THERMOLITE® in the footbox for additional warmth
Vertical chest baffles prevent down migration and cold spots
Two-way #5 YKK side / foot zips provide ventilation and allow bag to be used as a quilt
Oversized zip draft tube with anti-snag materials
3D side-wall baffle maximizes loft right to the edge of the bag
3D hood draws in tight when needed
Journey Jo2 has a neck collar draft tube to seal and trap warmth
Soft touch 20D lining fabric is lightweight and highly breathable, durable 30D Nylon shell
Includes Ultra-Sil™ Compression Bag for compact storage
Zip Coupling: This bag is designed to zip with another
